    "• Did it get flagged as violating the AI tool's policies?",
    "The proportion of responses from each tool that included each feature was calculated and compared.",
    "Pooling across tools, most of the responses (79%), encouraged the user to seek help and were empathic in nature.",
    "See Table 2 and S1 Table for full results.",
